item.title: 99s
item.dc:creator: @mod_taharok Taharok
item.description:
@mod_taharok wrote:

Getting the SC hammers for construction is pretty fast if you use a SC clan and have decent stats. You could probably get all the hammers in under 10 hours if you have maxed SC stats. SC hammers cut the price in half, so it’s well worth it. You can probably get 99 for around 70m, but it depends on whether you run planks (can take a very long time, even with CW and sawmill teleports), or buy the planks. You also have costs for making the butler unnote planks for you, unless you bank them yourself in yanille. Then, of course, there is the decision between oak and mahogany for skilling.

All in all, there are a lot of options. The fastest is probably SC hammers with purchased mahogany planks, but I believe that can border on costs over 100m. Just play around with cost and speed.
